1021001.name: Bunny Plushie
1021001.description: A pink stuffed bunny with a scarf. It's made of soft materials that make you want to hug it all day.

1021002.name: Romantic's Bouquet
1021002.description: This bouquet exudes a rich, captivating aroma. Both the roses and the other red flowers are practically dripping with emotion and romance.

1021003.name: Cake Gift Box
1021003.description: A meticulously wrapped box containing slices of delicious cake. You can eat them yourself, or you can gift them and make someone's day.

2022001.description: A toolbox of must-have items for cleaning and tidying up both at home and at the workplace. It's built with durable and resilient materials to protect the tools inside from damage.

2022002.description:
A classy, elegant tea set from the Royal Islands.
Its blue and white design feels both refreshing and relaxing, bringing grace to your teatime.
